聆听 Kesha 作为独立艺术家的第一首俏皮单曲：“JOYRIDE” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-kesha-debut-independent-song-joyride-3771070?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-kesha-debut-independent-song-joyrideKyann-Sian Williams Thu, 04 Jul 2024 16:34:17 +0000 Music NewsNewsDancePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3771070 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="WeHo Pride 的 Kesha。照片来源：Sarah Morris/WireImage" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “你说得对，我就是个贱人”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-kesha-debut-independent-song-joyride-3771070">聆听 Kesha 作为独立艺术家的第一首俏皮单曲：“JOYRIDE”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="WeHo Pride 的 Kesha。照片来源：Sarah Morris/WireImage" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kesha-Sarah-Morris_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/kesha">Kesha</a>分享了充满活力的“Joy Ride”，这是她与<a href="/artists/dr-luke">Dr. Luke</a>分道扬镳后作为独立艺术家的首张专辑。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/kesha-gag-order-rick-rubin-tik-tok-3445064">凯莎谈狂野的新专辑《Gag Order》：“当我感到被看到、听到和接受时，我很高兴”</a></li></ul><p>这首歌于今天发行，即美国独立日（7 月 4 日）。 《Joy Ride》与<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kesha-gag-order-review-3445135">《Gag Order》</a>的实验性质不同，《Gag Order》是她的第五张专辑，更接近艺术风格。然而，Kesha 的最新单曲是对她早期热门歌曲《Tik ToK》和《We R Who We R》中发现的合成器流行声音的回顾。</p><p> 《JOYRIDE》是一首充满活力的赞歌，凯莎拥抱了自己内心的“<em>婊子</em>”，毫无歉意地要求以粗暴和态度度过一个激动人心的夜晚。这首由 Zone 制作的歌曲中包含一些引述歌词，例如<em>“你想要孩子吗？好吧，我是妈妈”</em>和<em>“进来吧，失败者，去兜风”</em> ——最后一个是参考了 2004 年的经典电影《<a href="/films/mean-girls"><em>贱女孩》</em></a> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Kesha - JOYRIDE（歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bDpi8EdPMhU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>上周末，这位“TiK ToK”歌手在 Instagram 上发布了一段穿着不同红色套装的简短视频。起初，她模仿汽车，骑着敞篷车，对着镜头竖起中指，然后戴上红色牛仔帽，举起手写的写有“Joy Ride”的纸板牌。</p><p>这位流行歌星还分享了单曲的封面艺术，其中她穿着红色网状紧身裤和光滑的靴子坐在汽车引擎盖上。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C80Gm-XOsHH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px)