eImage 摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kesha-Musician-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kesha-Musician-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kesha-Musician-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kesha-Musician-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kesha-Musician-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kesha-Musician-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3762658" class="wp-caption-text">凯莎（莎拉·莫里斯/WireImage 摄）</figcaption></figure><p>离开 Kemosabe 唱片公司后，Kesha <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-teases-new-music-on-cardboard-sign-in-a-los-angeles-car-park-3565977">多次更新了她的新音乐</a>。近日，<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C8OkWZhONB1/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">她分享了一张她在Rick Rubin家中的照片</a>，暗示两人继《Gag Order》成功后再次合作。</p><p>今年早些时候，凯莎承认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-reveals-she-is-writing-new-music-ferociously-but-cant-release-it-just-yet-3589115">她正在“疯狂”地创作新音乐</a>，并在她的粉丝网站 keshaiswaitingforyou.com 的 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-teases-next-era-with-snippets-of-new-music-3597821">宣传视频中调侃了另一首歌——一首缓慢、空灵的民谣</a>。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-plays-her-first-show-as-a-free-motherfucking-woman-at-weho-pride-3762649">这位歌手以“自由自在的女人”身份在 WeHo Pride 举办了她的第一场演唱会</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-kesha-debut-independent-song-joyride-3771070">聆听 Kesha 作为独立艺术家的第一首俏皮单曲：“JOYRIDE”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
